ciscoPfcExtMIB.name: ciscoPfcExtMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoPfcExtMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-lan-switch-snmp@cisco.com
ciscoPfcExtMIB.description: This MIB module defines management objects for monitoring information of Priority-based Flow Control. The following terms are used throughout the MIB: PFC: Priority Flow Control

cpfcIfTable.name: cpfcIfTable
cpfcIfTable.description: A list of PFC informaton for each interface in the system capable of providing such information.

cpfcIfEntry.name: cpfcIfEntry
cpfcIfEntry.description: Each entry contains the PFC statistics information of the interface.

cpfcIfRequests.name: cpfcIfRequests
cpfcIfRequests.description: A count of the invoked PFC M_CONTROL.request primitives for a particular interface.

cpfcIfIndications.name: cpfcIfIndications
cpfcIfIndications.description: A count of the received PFC M_CONTROL.indication primitives for a particular interface.

cpfcIfPriorityTable.name: cpfcIfPriorityTable
cpfcIfPriorityTable.description: A list of PFC informaton for each PFC priority of each interface in the system capable of providing such information.

cpfcIfPriorityEntry.name: cpfcIfPriorityEntry
cpfcIfPriorityEntry.description: Each entry contains the PFC statistics information for a PFC priority of the interface.

cpfcIfPriorityValue.name: cpfcIfPriorityValue
cpfcIfPriorityValue.description: This object indicates the priority value of the PFC capable interface.

cpfcIfPriorityRequests.name: cpfcIfPriorityRequests
cpfcIfPriorityRequests.description: A count of invoked request premitives for a specific PFC priority of a particular interface.

cpfcIfPriorityIndications.name: cpfcIfPriorityIndications
cpfcIfPriorityIndications.description: A count of the received indication primitives for a specific PFC priority of a particular interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoTable.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoTable
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoTable.description: This table provides PFC Watchdog Timer related information for each queue of each watchdog timer capable interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoEntry.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoEntry
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueInfoEntry.description: Each entry contains the PFC Watchdog Time information, which are per interface and per queue.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueNumber.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueNumber
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueNumber.description: This object indicates the queue number of the interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueState.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueState
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueState.description: This object indicates the state of the PFC queue for the interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueShutdowns.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueShutdowns
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueShutdowns.description: This object indicates the number of times a given PFC queue was shutdown for the interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueRestores.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueRestores
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueRestores.description: This object indicates the number of times a given PFC queue was restored for the interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueTotalDropPkts.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueTotalDropPkts
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueTotalDropPkts.description: This object indicates total number of packets that were dropped due to corrective action for a given PFC queue of the interface.

cpfcWatchdogIfQueueDropPkts.name: cpfcWatchdogIfQueueDropPkts
cpfcWatchdogIfQueueDropPkts.description: This object indicates total number of packets that have been dropped due to corrective action since last shutdown action for a given PFC queue of the interface.

ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance.name: ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance
ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for the CISCO-PFC-EXT-MIB.

ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance2.name: ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance2
ciscoPfcExtMIBCompliance2.description: The compliance statement for the CISCO-PFC-EXT-MIB.

ciscoPfcExtIfGroup.name: ciscoPfcExtIfGroup
ciscoPfcExtIfGroup.description: A collection of objects that provides PFC information of each interface capable of providing such information.

ciscoPfcExtIfPriorityGroup.name: ciscoPfcExtIfPriorityGroup
ciscoPfcExtIfPriorityGroup.description: A collection of objects that provides PFC information of each PFC priority of an interface capable of providing such information.

ciscoPfcExtWatchdogIfQueueGroup.name: ciscoPfcExtWatchdogIfQueueGroup
ciscoPfcExtWatchdogIfQueueGroup.description: A collection of object(s) for PFC watchdog timer information of each queue of an interface capable of providing such information.
